==English==
===Noun phrase===
'''multiplication table''' (''plural'' '''multiplication tables''')

#{{arithmetic}} A [[table]] showing the [[product]]s of each of the [[integer]]s from 1 to 10 (or, especially formerly, 12) with each of the integers from 1 to 10 (or 12).

